HTTP verbs and routes for:

- a page with the form to create a new item
GET '/items/new'
- a route to create a new item
POST '/items'
- a page to see all of the new items
GET '/items'
- a page with a form to update an existing item
GET '/items/:id/edit'
- a route to update the item
PUT 'items/:id'
- a page to see an existing item
GET '/items/:id'
- a route to delete the item
DELETE 'items/:id'